name: SOD1 Spark Overdrive
details:
80's vintage overdrive toneClassic overdrive tones in a pedal perfect for any pedal board.
The Spark Overdrive creates '80s vintage overdrive tone perfectly suited for blues, classic rock and many more styles. Use it as a boost to push your amplifier or as a standalone overdrive/boost. Its full metal housing is built to take abuse and features a special surface treating technology, giving it maximum durability. It also features true bypass maximizes signal integrity when not in use. Power supply sold separately.
Features
* Vintage overdrive tones
* Boost capabilities
* Compact size
* Sturdy metal housing with special surface treatment
* True bypass
